bracket
Homonym Number:  1
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:to couple in a horse race for dividend payment purposes the horses of the same owner or trainer


Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: (revise this definition use HNZD2) racing in the same race.
